  ENG<br />
  Loneliness, fears and dealing with our demons is a recurrent theme in my work. I had this idea and thought it would look great as a T-shirt. So I endeavoured to produce some of them myself. I used phosphorescent ink so that they glow in the dark, it seemed very fitting. It was a very small batch for friends but if you want want hit me up, I might make more in the future.
  I made them on white and also on black fabric.
